response.original_title: The B1G Story: The Brands Brothers
response.overview: The story of two of the most polarizing wrestlers in the history of the sport, Tom and Terry Brands. See how these small-town Iowa twins grew up to become international wrestling stars, Olympic champions and distinguished coaches. Hear from legends in the sport like Dan Gable, John Smith and more about the impact of the Brands brothers on and off the mat.
response.tagline: When you stepped on the mat with Tom and Terry Brands, it was costly.
response.title: The B1G Story: The Brands Brothers
